-- FACTBOX: Family businesses in the United States
-- 
-- Fri May 11, 2007 2:36pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/05/11/us-family-factbox-idUSN1142246220070511

 

 CHICAGO  (Reuters) - Here are some facts about family businesses in the United States: 

 -- U.S. businesses that are family-controlled: 17 million to 22 million -- Percent of family businesses that pass successfully to the second generation: 35 percent -- Percent of family businesses that pass successfully to the third generation: 12 percent -- Percent of family businesses that pass successfully to the fourth generation: 4 percent -- U.S. work force employed with a family business: 80 percent SOURCE: University of St. Thomas